04:31:31.680 --> 04:31:36.160
[Guest]: rules. Plus there are other rules that the community itself has evolved like people who

04:31:36.160 --> 04:31:41.360
[Guest]: are practicing I mean driving in a particular road may have evolved some kind of a practice

04:31:41.360 --> 04:31:46.240
