[Amit Varma]: them really broadly is sort of the indian economy like in one of your recent newsletters you begin

05:12:55.120 --> 05:13:01.280
[Amit Varma]: by quoting this famous paper by robert lucas where he are a 1988 paper where he asked quote

05:13:01.280 --> 05:13:05.440
[Amit Varma]: is there some action a government of india could take that would lead the indian economy to grow

05:13:05.440 --> 05:13:11.600
[Amit Varma]: like indonesia's or egypt's if so what exactly if not what is it about the nature of india that

05:13:11.600 --> 05:13:16.240
[Amit Varma]: makes it so the consequences of human for human welfare involved in questions like these are

