05:46:12.400 --> 05:46:19.120
[Guest]: income the poorest state in the US so it's not even close in terms of where you are and we

05:46:19.120 --> 05:46:25.040
[Guest]: harp so much over this inequality as an issue so I always say like I never write about inequality

05:46:25.040 --> 05:46:30.080
[Guest]: in that in that sense I care about it in some ways some specific ways like gender inequality

