05:51:46.080 --> 05:51:52.640
[Guest]: things are arranged and creating the necessity of creating some baseline agreement on developmental

05:51:52.640 --> 05:51:58.400
[Guest]: issues across different levels of government is very important third is we need to focus more on

05:51:58.400 --> 05:52:03.200
[Guest]: the reality of political economy than just the de jure policies I mean those are important for

05:52:03.200 --> 05:52:08.000
[Guest]: sure and in some cases their change can also change reality but we need to take to reality

05:52:08.000 --> 05:52:12.720
[Guest]: which means we need to shape the incentives of people who take decisions and who invest

05:52:12.720 --> 05:52:16.880
[Guest]: and what what do they look at what are the signals they are looking for before investing and all of

05:52:16.880 --> 05:52:22.320
[Guest]: that what kind of signals do you want to send to that so the communications and narratives matter

05:52:22.320 --> 05:52:28.720
[Guest]: quite a bit I think and they will shape future expectations and you can have you can sustain

