[Guest]: growth then there is a I think it's quite important to in some senses do reforms you know

05:52:36.480 --> 05:52:40.480
[Guest]: but like for example we always talk about there are factor market reforms that are to be done in

05:52:40.480 --> 05:52:47.280
[Guest]: India and land labor all of that but in that we need to think more carefully about what are the

05:52:47.280 --> 05:52:52.880
