[Guest]: secularized society where religion has taken a very very small role in society and accepted that

05:58:36.960 --> 05:58:41.280
[Guest]: role for itself people who are religious also practice in very different ways you know from us

05:58:41.280 --> 05:58:45.840
[Guest]: we have a strong number of large number of people who true believers strong believers and very

05:58:45.840 --> 05:58:50.640
[Guest]: suspicious of other communities because they are very they're very deeply embedded in their

